Comment: 0,0:00:05.00,0:00:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
Comment: 0,0:00:07.00,0:00:08.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hey, Fuyuzora.
Comment: 0,0:00:09.67,0:00:11.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What's Yuuna like?
Comment: 0,0:00:12.63,0:00:15.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"Yuuna" is a girl's name, right?
Comment: 0,0:00:15.43,0:00:18.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I wonder if she's little like Koyuzu.
Comment: 0,0:00:18.01,0:00:21.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Or maybe she's about the same age as me?
Comment: 0,0:00:21.48,0:00:23.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,And I wonder what her face looks like.
Comment: 0,0:00:24.85,0:00:27.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,When I was imagining things about her,\Nit made me curious.
Comment: 0,0:00:29.57,0:00:31.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What's she like?
Comment: 0,0:00:31.78,0:00:33.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- Is she there right now?\N- Yeah.
Comment: 0,0:00:33.99,0:00:35.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm here!
Comment: 0,0:00:36.20,0:00:39.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Then can I try taking a picture?
Comment: 0,0:00:40.41,0:00:42.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Maybe it can capture her.
Comment: 0,0:00:43.92,0:00:45.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Um...
Comment: 0,0:00:45.33,0:00:49.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Sorry, it's difficult for me\Nto have my picture taken.
Comment: 0,0:00:52.67,0:00:54.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,She says she doesn't like\Nhaving her picture taken.
Comment: 0,0:00:55.14,0:00:56.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Is that so.
Comment: 0,0:00:57.05,0:00:58.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That's too bad.
Comment: 0,0:00:59.43,0:01:01.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Then can I talk to her?
Comment: 0,0:01:01.77,0:01:04.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I want to say thank you\Nfor Koyuzu's incident, too.
Comment: 0,0:01:04.35,0:01:07.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I want to try talking to Chisaki, too!
Comment: 0,0:01:07.81,0:01:09.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Easy for you to say...
Comment: 0,0:01:09.98,0:01:14.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It takes ten years of training\Nto be able to talk to ghosts.
Comment: 0,0:01:14.36,0:01:16.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,And also a near-death experience.
Comment: 0,0:01:16.61,0:01:19.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I don't think I'd want to gamble my life.
Comment: 0,0:01:20.49,0:01:22.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Well, I guess I could interpret.
Comment: 0,0:01:23.71,0:01:25.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Or wait, that's probably not necessary.
Comment: 0,0:01:30.13,0:01:32.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,The pen is moving by itself!
Comment: 0,0:01:32.76,0:01:35.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an5}NICE TO MEET YOU
Comment: 0,0:01:34.30,0:01:35.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you!
Comment: 0,0:01:36.26,0:01:38.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,We can communicate in writing.
Comment: 0,0:01:39.72,0:01:40.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Wow!
Comment: 0,0:01:40.93,0:01:43.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It's because Yuuna can touch things.
Comment: 0,0:01:43.02,0:01:45.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,This way we can talk about all kinds of things!
Comment: 0,0:01:45.60,0:01:50.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Right! I want to talk about\Nall kinds of things, too!
Comment: 0,0:03:21.41,0:03:24.95,Title,NTP,0,0,0,,Yuuna's Body Measurements
Comment: 0,0:03:25.08,0:03:29.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}You may not be familiar\Nwhen you hear the words "Ancient Orient,"
Comment: 0,0:03:29.21,0:03:32.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}but generally speaking, that includes everything\Nfrom the Arabian Peninsula to Egypt.
Comment: 0,0:03:31.58,0:03:35.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yuuna is talking to Miyazaki again.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:03:36.59,0:03:39.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Do they really have that much to talk about?{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:03:40.38,0:03:43.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Where are you usually, Yuuna?
Comment: 0,0:03:43.64,0:03:46.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yuragi Inn. Kogarashi is there, too.
Comment: 0,0:03:47.72,0:03:49.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,He's there, too?
Comment: 0,0:03:49.39,0:03:52.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What's your relationship to Fuyuzora?
Comment: 0,0:03:53.23,0:03:58.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm bound to a room in the inn\Nand Kogarashi moved in there.
Comment: 0,0:04:00.82,0:04:02.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,So what happened?
Comment: 0,0:04:02.49,0:04:05.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Kogarashi and I are living in the same room.
Comment: 0,0:04:07.62,0:04:09.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Fuyuzora!{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:04:09.54,0:04:12.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}What did Yuuna tell her?{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:04:15.46,0:04:19.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yuuna, are you dating Fuyuzora?
Comment: 0,0:04:20.17,0:04:22.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I-It's nothing like that!
Comment: 0,0:04:22.38,0:04:25.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm a ghost, for one thing,\Nand just the idea of dating...
Comment: 0,0:04:25.89,0:04:29.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Right? But still,\Nit's weird that you're roommates!
Comment: 0,0:04:33.90,0:04:34.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yuuna.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:04:36.48,0:04:39.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't hold back anymore.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:04:40.15,0:04:41.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kogarashi!{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:04:43.20,0:04:47.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,B-B-Because you never know\Nwhen he'll attack you like that!
Comment: 0,0:04:49.79,0:04:51.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Kogarashi isn't like that!
Comment: 0,0:04:51.71,0:04:56.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm sure Fuyuzora is a nice guy.\NBut Mom told me all men are wolves!
Comment: 0,0:04:53.87,0:04:54.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Miyazaki.
Comment: 0,0:04:56.42,0:04:57.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Miyazaki!
Comment: 0,0:04:57.84,0:04:58.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yes?
Comment: 0,0:04:59.05,0:05:01.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Miyazaki?\NWhy don't you read the next part out loud?
Comment: 0,0:05:01.97,0:05:04.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,S-Sorry. Starting where?
Comment: 0,0:05:04.47,0:05:06.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What? You're not focusing!
Comment: 0,0:05:06.09,0:05:09.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,As punishment, you're staying after school\Nto put away materials!
Comment: 0,0:05:07.89,0:05:12.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}I'm sorry! I'm sorry, Chisaki!
Comment: 0,0:05:10.56,0:05:12.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Comment: 0,0:05:12.60,0:05:14.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}What are they doing?{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:05:18.82,0:05:20.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}SOCIAL STUDIES MATERIALS ROOM
Comment: 0,0:05:23.49,0:05:25.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I finished!
Comment: 0,0:05:25.61,0:05:27.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Good work, Chisaki!
Comment: 0,0:05:28.24,0:05:31.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Sorry, Yuuna.\NI had you help me here.
Comment: 0,0:05:31.41,0:05:35.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Not at all. It was my fault to begin with.
Comment: 0,0:05:35.17,0:05:39.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for continuing our conversation\Nduring class time.
Comment: 0,0:05:39.13,0:05:42.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,No! This is what I get.
Comment: 0,0:05:42.88,0:05:49.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Even though you can't see me, you're the first\Nperson who's ever talked to me like this,
Comment: 0,0:05:49.39,0:05:51.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,so I couldn't help being excited.
Comment: 0,0:05:54.64,0:05:55.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Comment: 0,0:05:56.31,0:06:02.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I got it. I want to do something to thank you\Nfor helping me clean up.
Comment: 0,0:06:04.44,0:06:06.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wonder what this is made of.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:06:08.78,0:06:11.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I know! You wanted to examine\Nmy school uniform, right?
Comment: 0,0:06:11.74,0:06:12.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Y-Yes.
Comment: 0,0:06:13.16,0:06:15.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Then you can touch me wherever you want.
Comment: 0,0:06:15.83,0:06:17.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Really?
Comment: 0,0:06:17.50,0:06:20.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,But I'm a ghost...
Comment: 0,0:06:21.38,0:06:25.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,so wouldn't it be creepy for me to touch you?
Comment: 0,0:06:27.51,0:06:29.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,No, not at all!
Comment: 0,0:06:29.84,0:06:33.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,This is my way of showing thanks,\Nso don't hold back! Touch me!
Comment: 0,0:06:35.64,0:06:37.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Comment: 0,0:06:44.61,0:06:46.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sh-She's touching me.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:06:47.61,0:06:51.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}It feels weird to be touched\Nby someone I can't see.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:06:53.08,0:06:55.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I WILL NOW TAKE YOUR UNIFORM OFF!
Comment: 0,0:07:10.18,0:07:12.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wonder where she's looking now?{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:07:14.18,0:07:16.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I know Yuuna is a girl, but...{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:07:19.06,0:07:24.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}this might be a little embarrassing after all!{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:07:27.28,0:07:29.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Thank you!
Comment: 0,0:07:29.24,0:07:32.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Thanks to you, I was able to fully examine it.
Comment: 0,0:07:32.74,0:07:35.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}R-Really? That's good.
Comment: 0,0:07:35.83,0:07:37.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,But it's a shame.
Comment: 0,0:07:37.79,0:07:42.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Even if you can wear a school uniform,\NI can't see you in it.
Comment: 0,0:07:43.08,0:07:46.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I still don't know what you look like, Yuuna.
Comment: 0,0:07:57.47,0:08:01.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm making it so you can touch me,\Nso please do.
Comment: 0,0:08:01.48,0:08:04.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,This way you might be able\Nto picture me a little.
Comment: 0,0:08:12.78,0:08:14.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}She has nice facial features.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:08:22.92,0:08:27.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}A slim waist, delicate shoulders, and silky hair.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:08:27.80,0:08:29.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Such a nice figure!{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:08:30.55,0:08:33.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm sure she's a beautiful girl.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:08:34.51,0:08:35.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Miyazaki!
Comment: 0,0:08:35.93,0:08:36.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yuuna!
Comment: 0,0:08:39.68,0:08:40.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I figured I'd help—
Comment: 0,0:08:49.23,0:08:50.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,At least knock first!
Comment: 0,0:08:50.53,0:08:52.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Don't just suddenly barge in!
Comment: 0,0:08:52.20,0:08:54.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- Wh-What the hell are you two doing?\N- No!
Comment: 0,0:08:56.95,0:09:00.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,All right, take a look at this!
Comment: 0,0:09:02.91,0:09:05.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,How do I look, Kogarashi and Chisaki?
Comment: 0,0:09:06.17,0:09:07.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That's perfect!
Comment: 0,0:09:08.38,0:09:10.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I still can't see you.
Comment: 0,0:09:10.55,0:09:12.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,This is thanks to you, Chisaki!
Comment: 0,0:09:14.68,0:09:17.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yuuna, don't float around so much\Nwhen you're wearing that.
Comment: 0,0:09:18.60,0:09:22.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yuuna, why don't you like\Ngetting your picture taken?
Comment: 0,0:09:24.56,0:09:29.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Sorry. I was just thinking it'd be nice\Nif we could take a picture together.
Comment: 0,0:09:30.48,0:09:32.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It's not a big deal.
Comment: 0,0:09:32.78,0:09:38.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It's just that I don't show up clearly in pictures,\Nand it scares people.
Comment: 0,0:09:40.49,0:09:41.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I see.
Comment: 0,0:09:42.58,0:09:45.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I have this idea that\Npictures don't only capture the people,
Comment: 0,0:09:45.58,0:09:47.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,but when you look at them later,
Comment: 0,0:09:47.42,0:09:53.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,they remind you of the scents, temperature,\Nand even feelings of that moment.
Comment: 0,0:09:56.18,0:09:58.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I won't be afraid after all this!
Comment: 0,0:09:58.80,0:10:00.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,So let's take one!
Comment: 0,0:10:00.06,0:10:01.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Okay!
Comment: 0,0:10:02.47,0:10:03.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Come right here.
Comment: 0,0:10:03.60,0:10:04.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,R-Right!
Comment: 0,0:10:04.73,0:10:05.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,H-Hey!
Comment: 0,0:10:05.85,0:10:07.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Say cheese!
Comment: 0,0:10:13.65,0:10:16.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- So that's how she shows up.\N- I-It's scary, isn't it?
Comment: 0,0:10:16.99,0:10:21.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}I-It's all right!\NCertainly, as is, it's a little scary...
Comment: 0,0:10:22.91,0:10:24.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}But look! Isn't it cute?
Comment: 0,0:10:30.63,0:10:31.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yuuna?
Comment: 0,0:10:31.42,0:10:33.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,H-Huh? You don't like it?
Comment: 0,0:10:42.97,0:10:43.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,T-h-
Comment: 0,0:10:45.35,0:10:48.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-a-n-k-y-o-u.
Comment: 0,0:11:11.38,0:11:15.38,Title,NTP,0,0,0,,Nonko's Crunch Time
Comment: 0,0:11:12.38,0:11:13.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}I'm back!
Comment: 0,0:11:14.30,0:11:16.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}I'm home!
Comment: 0,0:11:16.72,0:11:18.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh, welcome home!
Comment: 0,0:11:19.47,0:11:21.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I just had a wonderful bath.
Comment: 0,0:11:22.10,0:11:25.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, you're always here\Nat Yuragi Inn, aren't you, Nonko?
Comment: 0,0:11:25.85,0:11:27.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Actually, Nonko is...
Comment: 0,0:11:27.60,0:11:28.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Sensei!
Comment: 0,0:11:30.15,0:11:32.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nonko-sensei! I've been looking for you!
Comment: 0,0:11:33.40,0:11:34.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Rui!
Comment: 0,0:11:34.57,0:11:37.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Don't tell me you were taking a bath\Nduring deadline crunch?
Comment: 0,0:11:37.69,0:11:40.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I wanted to be refreshed.
Comment: 0,0:11:40.28,0:11:42.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nonko... sensei?
Comment: 0,0:11:43.28,0:11:46.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh, pardon me.\NAre you a resident of Yuragi Inn?
Comment: 0,0:11:46.54,0:11:47.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yes.
Comment: 0,0:11:48.29,0:11:54.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm Rui Harashima, Arahabaki-sensei's chief editor.
Comment: 0,0:11:54.63,0:11:56.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Monthly Girls' Marmalade?
Comment: 0,0:11:57.21,0:11:58.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That means Nonko is...
Comment: 0,0:11:59.76,0:12:01.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,...a manga artist?
Comment: 0,0:12:01.01,0:12:05.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That's right. I actually have a job.
Comment: 0,0:12:05.26,0:12:07.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}ROOM 201
Comment: 0,0:12:06.10,0:12:07.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Comment: 0,0:12:08.27,0:12:12.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Welcome! It's a bit messy, though.
Comment: 0,0:12:13.94,0:12:16.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,As always.
Comment: 0,0:12:16.65,0:12:20.61,MidR,NTP,0,0,0,,MOUNTAINS\NAND SEAS
Comment: 0,0:12:16.65,0:12:20.61,MidC,NTP,0,0,0,,FALL FESTIVAL
Comment: 0,0:12:16.65,0:12:20.61,MidL,NTP,0,0,0,,OGRE KILLER
Comment: 0,0:12:17.44,0:12:20.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I think there's more alcohol here than last time.
Comment: 0,0:12:22.82,0:12:25.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,So what's this about deadline crunch?
Comment: 0,0:12:25.49,0:12:29.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nonko-sensei's at-home assistant is in the hospital,\Nrecovering from an accident.
Comment: 0,0:12:30.29,0:12:33.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,She's supposed to get out sometime next week.
Comment: 0,0:12:34.67,0:12:38.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,but this month's deadline is tomorrow.
Comment: 0,0:12:39.05,0:12:40.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Tomorrow?
Comment: 0,0:12:40.17,0:12:43.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,To be more precise,\Nit's tomorrow morning at 7:00 am.
Comment: 0,0:12:43.26,0:12:44.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,She has 15 hours left.
Comment: 0,0:12:45.72,0:12:48.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,And yet there are still several blank pages.
Comment: 0,0:12:48.89,0:12:51.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Isn't she in hot water?
Comment: 0,0:12:51.43,0:12:52.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Incredibly hot.
Comment: 0,0:12:53.85,0:12:57.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Please help me, Kogarashi!
Comment: 0,0:12:57.52,0:12:59.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Fine.
Comment: 0,0:12:59.32,0:13:02.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'll help you to the best of my ability, too!
Comment: 0,0:13:02.36,0:13:04.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Thank you, both of you!
Comment: 0,0:13:04.86,0:13:07.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'll do my best!
Comment: 0,0:13:09.54,0:13:11.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}I LIVE FOR THIS ONE CUP
Comment: 0,0:13:09.54,0:13:11.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}NO BOOZE UNTIL WORK IS DONE
Comment: 0,0:13:09.54,0:13:11.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,SEALED SEALED SEALED
Comment: 0,0:13:13.92,0:13:17.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Eeek! Thump-thump-thump-thump..."
Comment: 0,0:13:17.67,0:13:21.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}How many times are you going\Nto swoon over the same person?
Comment: 0,0:13:20.13,0:13:23.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Does Nonko seem different to you?
Comment: 0,0:13:22.05,0:13:24.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}I mean, is your cardiovascular system okay?
Comment: 0,0:13:23.51,0:13:27.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,When she's working on a manuscript,\Nespecially before deadline, she gets pretty rough.
Comment: 0,0:13:27.89,0:13:31.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,But when she's in the zone like that,\Nshe manages to get it done in time.
Comment: 0,0:13:32.43,0:13:34.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I've never seen Nonko like this before.
Comment: 0,0:13:35.35,0:13:38.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,By the way, Fuyuzora, you're good.
Comment: 0,0:13:38.52,0:13:40.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Do you make your own manga?
Comment: 0,0:13:40.44,0:13:44.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Well, a long time ago I was possessed\Nby the ghost of an aspiring manga artist.
Comment: 0,0:13:44.90,0:13:45.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,A ghost?
Comment: 0,0:13:46.82,0:13:52.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,But Nonko created this manga.\NSo she has interests outside of alcohol, huh?
Comment: 0,0:13:54.37,0:13:55.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nonko?
Comment: 0,0:13:55.46,0:13:59.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Even though this boy is pursued\Nby a cadre of charming girls,
Comment: 0,0:13:59.84,0:14:03.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,besides the female lead character,\Nhe doesn't recognize their femininity.
Comment: 0,0:14:04.09,0:14:05.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,He never wavers in that regard.
Comment: 0,0:14:06.43,0:14:10.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,He'd never betray her.
Comment: 0,0:14:11.01,0:14:12.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ever.
Comment: 0,0:14:13.14,0:14:16.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Such a single-minded man can't exist!
Comment: 0,0:14:16.48,0:14:18.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You're the one who's drawing it!
Comment: 0,0:14:18.94,0:14:26.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Why do I have to create an elaborate depiction\Nof love-struck, squealing, giggling teens?
Comment: 0,0:14:26.57,0:14:29.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm an adult, damn it!
Comment: 0,0:14:29.78,0:14:31.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Should we not intervene?
Comment: 0,0:14:31.91,0:14:36.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nonko-sensei channels her frustrations\Ninto the manuscript,
Comment: 0,0:14:36.83,0:14:39.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,but once in a while\Nshe's reminded of reality and gets like this.
Comment: 0,0:14:44.96,0:14:46.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Manga artists are so...
Comment: 0,0:14:56.94,0:14:58.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Now what's wrong?
Comment: 0,0:14:58.44,0:15:01.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm stuck on an entanglement scene.
Comment: 0,0:15:01.98,0:15:04.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm bad at rough sketches.
Comment: 0,0:15:04.73,0:15:10.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh. the scene where the main character\Nis attacked by the aggressive boy?
Comment: 0,0:15:10.20,0:15:12.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,There's a scene like that in girls' manga?
Comment: 0,0:15:12.74,0:15:14.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It's there because it's girls' manga!
Comment: 0,0:15:14.79,0:15:21.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That's it! Since I've got you here, Kogarashi,\Ncan I take reference photos?
Comment: 0,0:15:22.13,0:15:24.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Reference photos?
Comment: 0,0:15:29.51,0:15:31.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Okay, Kogarashi!
Comment: 0,0:15:31.80,0:15:34.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Go ahead and attack me, please.
Comment: 0,0:15:34.89,0:15:36.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,This is all sorts of danger!
Comment: 0,0:15:36.56,0:15:39.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,And was it really necessary to change clothes?
Comment: 0,0:15:39.69,0:15:41.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It's better as a reference that way.
Comment: 0,0:15:42.56,0:15:45.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Okay, we're going to snap away!
Comment: 0,0:15:47.11,0:15:50.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Kogarashi, put your arms\Nall the way around my waist.
Comment: 0,0:15:50.36,0:15:51.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,O-Okay.
Comment: 0,0:15:55.79,0:15:59.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Fuyuzora doesn't seem like he's into it.
Comment: 0,0:15:59.46,0:16:00.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Comment: 0,0:16:00.83,0:16:03.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I want it to be more like you're ravaging me.
Comment: 0,0:16:03.75,0:16:05.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Comment: 0,0:16:05.71,0:16:10.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,All right. Try putting your hand under my skirt.
Comment: 0,0:16:11.89,0:16:14.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Uh, I don't think I can.
Comment: 0,0:16:14.05,0:16:16.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh, Kogarashi.
Comment: 0,0:16:16.47,0:16:19.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Don't be so embarrassed.
Comment: 0,0:16:19.56,0:16:22.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It's making me feel bashful, too.
Comment: 0,0:16:22.90,0:16:25.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Remember, this is just for reference photos.
Comment: 0,0:16:27.53,0:16:30.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's right. This is Nonko's work.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:16:31.28,0:16:32.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have to do it right.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:16:33.53,0:16:35.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Sorry I haven't been focusing.
Comment: 0,0:16:35.95,0:16:37.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}I won't hesitate anymore.
Comment: 0,0:16:37.33,0:16:38.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That's the spirit!
Comment: 0,0:16:38.83,0:16:40.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's such a serious boy.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:16:40.96,0:16:43.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,O-Okay, here I go!
Comment: 0,0:16:43.00,0:16:45.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Comment: 0,0:16:45.54,0:16:46.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,L-Like this?
Comment: 0,0:16:46.50,0:16:49.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah! That's perfect!
Comment: 0,0:16:51.26,0:16:53.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Now rip my blouse off!
Comment: 0,0:16:53.47,0:16:54.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Right!
Comment: 0,0:16:55.14,0:16:56.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- Push me onto the bed!\N- Okay!
Comment: 0,0:17:01.39,0:17:02.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ow.
Comment: 0,0:17:05.81,0:17:09.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- S-Sorry!\N- Don't move away!
Comment: 0,0:17:09.65,0:17:13.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Rui, get a high-angle shot from there and there!
Comment: 0,0:17:13.20,0:17:14.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Right!
Comment: 0,0:17:14.03,0:17:16.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Change the angle a bit for multiple patterns!
Comment: 0,0:17:16.20,0:17:17.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Understood!
Comment: 0,0:17:17.70,0:17:19.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Is this what it means to be an adult?"{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:17:20.66,0:17:24.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kogarashi was slightly astonished.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:17:24.92,0:17:28.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,While we're at it, should we take crossdressing\Nreference photos for the culture festival scene?
Comment: 0,0:17:28.84,0:17:30.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Good idea!
Comment: 0,0:17:31.76,0:17:35.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}However, at midnight...{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:17:39.31,0:17:41.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh, it's 12 already?
Comment: 0,0:17:41.22,0:17:43.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,We're not making any progress on the manuscript!
Comment: 0,0:17:44.60,0:17:46.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}"I'll never become an adult like that."{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:17:47.48,0:17:50.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's what he swore to himself.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:17:55.53,0:17:56.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I poured you another cup of coffee.
Comment: 0,0:17:56.91,0:17:58.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Comment: 0,0:17:59.53,0:18:01.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Shouldn't we wake her up?
Comment: 0,0:18:01.91,0:18:05.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Rui's real work is after the manuscript is done.
Comment: 0,0:18:05.75,0:18:08.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Besides, thanks to her, I think I'll make it.
Comment: 0,0:18:08.79,0:18:09.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Good to hear.
Comment: 0,0:18:09.92,0:18:12.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I wasn't sure what would happen.
Comment: 0,0:18:13.38,0:18:19.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Come to think of it, Nonko hasn't had a drop\Nof alcohol while working on the manga.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:18:21.10,0:18:24.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nonko, you really love this work, don't you?
Comment: 0,0:18:25.52,0:18:27.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I wonder about that.
Comment: 0,0:18:30.48,0:18:35.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I actually used to be a youkai hunter\Nlike Sagi a long time ago.
Comment: 0,0:18:35.90,0:18:37.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh, really?
Comment: 0,0:18:40.53,0:18:44.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It was like the destiny of an ogre's descendant.
Comment: 0,0:18:45.79,0:18:52.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Back then, I was a good girl, so I did\Nas I was told. I did my best to fight youkai.
Comment: 0,0:18:57.80,0:19:02.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,But one day, after I messed up\Nand got badly hurt, I thought about something.
Comment: 0,0:19:03.06,0:19:08.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"Is my life going to end like this,\Nwithout having done anything?"
Comment: 0,0:19:10.11,0:19:13.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I think what happened afterwards\Nwas a reaction to that.
Comment: 0,0:19:13.32,0:19:17.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I felt like I wouldn't be satisfied\Nunless I did all the things I wanted to do.
Comment: 0,0:19:19.49,0:19:24.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,While doing different things,\NI settled on this work.
Comment: 0,0:19:26.71,0:19:33.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}But in the end, maybe I'm just\Nrunning away from the battle.
Comment: 0,0:19:36.21,0:19:39.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nah, I don't think so.
Comment: 0,0:19:41.72,0:19:46.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,After all, Nonko, can you hold back\Nfor youkai hunting too?
Comment: 0,0:19:49.27,0:19:50.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Drinking.
Comment: 0,0:19:54.82,0:19:56.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Sensei...
Comment: 0,0:19:56.94,0:19:59.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}To Nonko Arahabaki-sensei <3\NNice to meet you!\NI'm a second-year middle school girl\Nwho always looks forward\Nto reading your manga!
Comment: 0,0:20:05.37,0:20:07.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I don't think I could.
Comment: 0,0:20:10.25,0:20:11.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Okay!
Comment: 0,0:20:11.83,0:20:13.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Two hours until deadline!
Comment: 0,0:20:13.92,0:20:17.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,After I finish this manuscript,\NI’ll take a bath and drink!
Comment: 0,0:20:17.30,0:20:18.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,All right!
Comment: 0,0:20:24.30,0:20:26.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I have received the manuscript!
Comment: 0,0:20:26.85,0:20:30.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Well, I must take my leave!\NThank you for your efforts this month!
Comment: 0,0:20:32.94,0:20:35.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It's done. Good work.
Comment: 0,0:20:36.52,0:20:39.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Well, I'm going to bed.
Comment: 0,0:20:42.70,0:20:44.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Cheers!
Comment: 0,0:20:49.79,0:20:53.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}A beer after finishing my manuscript!\NThis is bliss!
Comment: 0,0:20:53.38,0:20:55.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Wait, you're going to start drinking now?
Comment: 0,0:20:55.38,0:20:56.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I want to sleep.
Comment: 0,0:20:56.92,0:21:00.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh, come on! Didn't I work hard?
Comment: 0,0:21:00.63,0:21:05.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- Let's celebrate together!\N- Hey! Are you drunk already?
Comment: 0,0:21:05.43,0:21:08.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I won't let you go until you say "Yeah."
Comment: 0,0:21:08.35,0:21:10.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,All right! All right, already!
Comment: 0,0:21:11.18,0:21:14.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nonko, your editor left.
Comment: 0,0:21:14.56,0:21:16.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Did you finish your work?
Comment: 0,0:21:17.23,0:21:19.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Everyone! Good morning!
Comment: 0,0:21:24.53,0:21:26.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Kogarashi Fuyuzora!
Comment: 0,0:21:26.83,0:21:28.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What were you doing here?
Comment: 0,0:21:28.54,0:21:30.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I was just helping!
Comment: 0,0:21:30.45,0:21:32.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Wait, Sagiri!
Comment: 0,0:21:32.33,0:21:34.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm sure Nonko is drunk again.
Comment: 0,0:21:34.50,0:21:35.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,All right!
Comment: 0,0:21:36.08,0:21:39.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Then let's all celebrate together!
Comment: 0,0:21:40.01,0:21:41.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Why is she stripping?
Comment: 0,0:21:41.63,0:21:44.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,This always happens\Nwhen she finishes her work.
Comment: 0,0:21:44.97,0:21:48.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,All right! I'm going to drink some more!
Comment: 0,0:21:48.30,0:21:51.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nonko! Just please put your clothes back on!
Comment: 0,0:21:52.56,0:21:56.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,We should all get naked together!
Comment: 0,0:21:56.15,0:22:00.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Little did Kogarashi know\Nthat he would get roped into helping out{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:22:00.32,0:22:03.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}during deadline crunch\Nnow and then after that.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:23:34.95,0:23:39.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Next time: Ms. Nakai's Secret Adventure\Nand A Sweet Day Off with Yuuna
Comment: 0,0:23:36.66,0:23:37.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Don't miss...
Comment: 0,0:23:37.75,0:23:39.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,the next episode!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.00,0:00:08.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nè, Fuyuzora-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.67,0:00:11.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yuuna-san là người như thế nào?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.63,0:00:15.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"Yuuna" là tên con gái mà phải không?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.43,0:00:18.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Không biết cô ấy còn nhỏ như Koyuzu-chan,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.01,0:00:21.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,hay là tầm tuổi tớ nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.48,0:00:23.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Rồi còn mặt mũi cô ấy trông như thế nào nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.85,0:00:27.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Càng tưởng tượng mấy thứ về cô ấy, tớ lại càng tò mò.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.57,0:00:31.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Trông như nào ấy nhỉ...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.78,0:00:33.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Giờ cô ấy đang ở đây à?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.99,0:00:35.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mình ở đây nè.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.20,0:00:39.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Vậy để tớ chụp thử tấm hình nhé?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.41,0:00:42.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Biết đâu nó chụp được thì sao.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.33,0:00:49.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Xin lỗi, muốn chụp được tớ thì khó lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.67,0:00:54.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Cậu ấy nói là không muốn bị chụp hình.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.14,0:00:56.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Thế à?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.05,0:00:58.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Tiếc thật.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.43,0:01:01.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Vậy trò chuyện với cô ấy được chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.77,0:01:04.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Tớ cũng muốn cảm ơn cô ấy vụ Koyuzu-chan nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.35,0:01:07.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mình cũng muốn thử nói chuyện với Chisaki-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.81,0:01:09.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nói như dễ lắm ấy...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.98,0:01:14.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Muốn trò chuyện với âm linh thì phải chịu khó tu luyện 10 năm nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.36,0:01:16.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mà phải là tu luyện như trâu như bò luôn ấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.61,0:01:19.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Đánh đổi cuộc đời tới mức đó thì có hơi...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.49,0:01:22.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Thôi thì để tớ làm thông ngôn cũng được.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.71,0:01:25.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,À khoan, đâu cần phải vậy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.13,0:01:32.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Cây bút tự di chuyển ư?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.72,0:01:35.80,Sign,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2\fs80\b0\fscx102\fscy105\pos(746,542)\frz20.16\c&H444545&}Hân hạnh được gặp cậu!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.30,0:01:35.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hân hạnh được gặp cậu!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.26,0:01:38.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Bọn mình có thể trò chuyện bằng văn bản mà!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.72,0:01:40.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ghê thiệt!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.93,0:01:43.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yuuna có thể chạm vào đồ vật mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.02,0:01:45.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Thế này thì bọn tớ có thể trao đổi được nhiều chuyện rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.60,0:01:50.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Vâng! Mình cũng muốn trò chuyện thiệt là nhiều!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.10,0:03:24.95,Title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,00)}SỐ ĐO CƠ THỂ CỦA YUUNA-SAN
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.08,0:03:29.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Có thể cụm từ "Cận Đông cổ đại" vẫn còn lạ với các em,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.21,0:03:32.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}nhưng nói chung, khu vực này kéo dài từ bán đảo Ả Rập đến Ai Cập.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.58,0:03:35.92,Default - Italics,NTP,0,0,0,,Nhỏ Yuuna với Miyazaki lại chuyện trò gì với nhau nữa à...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.59,0:03:39.05,Default - Italics,NTP,0,0,0,,2 người họ có nhiều chuyện để nói vậy à?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.38,0:03:43.18,Default - Italics,NTP,0,0,0,,Thường ngày Yuuna-san ở đâu?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.64,0:03:46.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nhà trọ Yuragi, Kogarashi-san cũng ở đó luôn.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.72,0:03:49.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Cũng ở đó?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.39,0:03:52.40,Default - Italics,NTP,0,0,0,,Quan hệ giữa 2 hai người là như nào?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.23,0:03:58.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Tớ là hồn ma bị chôn chân trong 1 phòng trọ, và Kogarashi-san đã thuê trọ phòng ấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.82,0:04:02.49,Default - Italics,NTP,0,0,0,,Sau đó thế nào?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.49,0:04:05.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Giờ bọn mình đang ở chung phòng.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.62,0:04:09.12,Default - Italics,NTP,0,0,0,,Fuyuzora-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.54,0:04:12.04,Default - Italics,NTP,0,0,0,,Con nhỏ Yuuna đó nói cái gì thế không biết!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.46,0:04:19.46,Default - Italics,NTP,0,0,0,,Yuuna-san, cậu đang hẹn hò với Fuyuzora-kun à?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.17,0:04:22.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,L-Làm gì có chứ!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.38,0:04:25.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mình là ma, nên mấy chuyện hẹn hò đó...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.89,0:04:29.64,Default - Italics,NTP,0,0,0,,Phải rồi ha? Nhưng chuyện hai người ở chung phòng thì kỳ lắm đó!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.90,0:04:34.94,Default - Flashback,NTP,0,0,0,,Yuuna!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.48,0:04:39.53,Default - Flashback,NTP,0,0,0,,Anh không chịu nổi nữa...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.15,0:04:41.40,Default - Flashback,NTP,0,0,0,,Kogarashi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.20,0:04:47.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,N-N-Nếu cậu ấy mà "tiến tới" như thế thì kỳ lắm đó!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.79,0:04:51.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Kogarashi-san không phải người như thế đâu!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.71,0:04:56.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Tớ biết Fuyuzora-kun là người tốt, nhưng mẹ tớ bảo đàn ông chỉ là lũ lang sói, rồi còn...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.87,0:04:54.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Miyazaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.42,0:04:57.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Miyazaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.84,0:04:58.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Vâng!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.05,0:05:01.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Chuyện gì thế Miyazaki?\NĐọc phần tiếp theo đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.97,0:05:04.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,E-Em xin lỗi.\NĐọc từ chỗ nào ạ?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.47,0:05:06.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Gì cơ? Không tập trung bài à?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.09,0:05:09.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Tan trường em ở lại xếp tài liệu cho tôi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.89,0:05:12.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Mình xin lỗi, Chisaki-san, mình xin lỗi...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.56,0:05:12.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Vâng...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.60,0:05:14.48,Default - Italics,NTP,0,0,0,,Hai người họ làm cái gì thế không biết...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.49,0:05:25.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Xong rồi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.61,0:05:27.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Cậu vất vả rồi, Chisaki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.24,0:05:31.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Xin lỗi nhé, Yuuna-san, đã để cậu phải giúp thế này.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.41,0:05:35.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Không, cũng do mình cả mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.17,0:05:39.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Xin lỗi cậu và đang trong giờ học mà vẫn còn nói chuyện...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.13,0:05:42.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Không đâu, chuyện đó mình tự làm tự chịu mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.88,0:05:49.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Dù không thấy được mình, nhưng cậu là người đầu tiên nói chuyện với mình như thế.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.39,0:05:51.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nên là mình có hơi quá khích.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.31,0:06:02.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Phải rồi, tớ muốn làm gì đó để cảm ơn cậu vì đã phụ tớ sắp xếp tài liệu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.44,0:06:06.78,Default - Flashback,NTP,0,0,0,,Không biết cái này được làm từ gì nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.78,0:06:11.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Phải rồi, cậu muốn tìm hiểu về đồng phục phải không?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.74,0:06:12.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,V-Vâng.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.16,0:06:15.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Vậy cứ sờ người tớ chỗ nào tuỳ thích.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.83,0:06:17.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Được à?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.50,0:06:20.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nhưng mình là ma...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.38,0:06:25.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,nên chạm vào cậu như thế, liệu có sao không?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.51,0:06:29.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Không sao đâu mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.84,0:06:33.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Đây gọi là tạ lễ mà, nào, không cần phải ngại, cậu cứ tự nhiên.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.64,0:06:37.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Cảm ơn cậu nhiều!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.61,0:06:46.82,Default - Italics,NTP,0,0,0,,C-Cậu ấy đang sờ người mình...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.61,0:06:51.91,Default - Italics,NTP,0,0,0,,Bị một người không thấy được sờ soạng, cảm giác kỳ thật đấy...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.08,0:06:55.33,Sign,NTP,0,0,0,,{\b0\blur5\fs80\frz27.02\pos(818,408)\c&H565754&}Giờ mình cởi đồng phục của cậu ra nhé!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.18,0:07:12.72,Default - Italics,NTP,0,0,0,,Giờ cậu ấy đang nhìn chỗ nào thế không biết...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.18,0:07:16.85,Default - Italics,NTP,0,0,0,,Mình biết Yuuna-san cũng là con gái, nhưng...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.06,0:07:24.19,Default - Italics,NTP,0,0,0,,đúng là làm thế này thì có hơi xấu hổ...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.28,0:07:29.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Cảm ơn cậu nhiều.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.24,0:07:32.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nhờ cậu mà tớ đã hiểu rõ nó rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.74,0:07:35.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,T-Thế à? Thế thì tốt.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.83,0:07:37.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nhưng tiếc thật nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.79,0:07:42.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Dù cậu có mặc được đồng phục thì tớ cũng chẳng thể thấy được.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.08,0:07:46.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mặt mũi cậu ra sao tớ còn chưa biết mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.47,0:08:01.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Sờ rồi cậu sẽ biết mình trông như thế nào thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.48,0:08:04.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Bằng cách này cậu có thể hình dung được chút ít rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.78,0:08:14.99,Default - Italics,NTP,0,0,0,,Cậu ấy có đủ các đặc điểm của một mỹ nhân...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.92,0:08:27.34,Default - Italics,NTP,0,0,0,,Eo thon, vai nhỏ và mái tóc mượt mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.80,0:08:29.26,Default - Italics,NTP,0,0,0,,Thân hình quá đẹp!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.55,0:08:33.97,Default - Italics,NTP,0,0,0,,Nhất định cậu ấy là một cô gái rất đẹp!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.51,0:08:35.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Miyazaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.93,0:08:36.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yuuna!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.68,0:08:40.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Tớ nghĩ mình có thể phụ—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.23,0:08:50.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ít nhất phải gõ cửa cho người ta biết chứ!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.53,0:08:52.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Đừng có tự dưng vào luôn chứ!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.20,0:08:54.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- Hai người đang làm cái quái gì thế?!\N- Không!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.95,0:09:00.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Vậy, 2 người nhìn cho kỹ nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.91,0:09:05.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Trông mình thế nào, Kogarashi-san, Chisaki-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.17,0:09:07.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Quá hợp luôn chứ sao.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.38,0:09:10.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Đúng là hổng thấy được.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.55,0:09:12.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nhờ Chisaki-san hết đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.68,0:09:17.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yuuna, ăn mặc như thế thì đừng có bay đi lung tung đấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.60,0:09:22.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yuuna-san, sao cậu lại không thích chụp hình?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.56,0:09:29.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Xin lỗi, tớ chỉ nghĩ rằng nếu bọn mình chụp chung 1 tấm thì còn gì bằng...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.48,0:09:32.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Không phải chuyện gì to tát đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.78,0:09:38.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Chỉ là hình dạng mình trong ảnh hiện không rõ, nên sẽ khiến mọi người sợ.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.49,0:09:41.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ra vậy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.58,0:09:45.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ảnh chụp không chỉ lưu lại hình ảnh con người,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.58,0:09:47.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,mà nó còn giúp ta sau này, khi nhìn vào,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.42,0:09:53.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,thì sẽ nhớ lại mùi hương, nhiệt độ, và cả những cảm xúc khi ấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.18,0:09:58.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mấy chuyện đó tớ không sợ đâu!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.80,0:10:00.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nên là mình chụp 1 tấm nhé?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.06,0:10:01.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Vâng!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.47,0:10:03.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Cậu đứng vào đây nhé!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.60,0:10:04.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,V-Vâng.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.73,0:10:05.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,N-Này!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.85,0:10:07.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Cười lên nào!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.65,0:10:16.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- Biết ngay sẽ thành ra vậy mà.\N- Đáng sợ lắm phải không?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.99,0:10:21.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,K-Không sao! Đúng là để thế này thì có hơi đáng sợ...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.91,0:10:24.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Xem này, đáng yêu không nè?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.63,0:10:31.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yuuna?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.38,0:10:33.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Cậu không thích à?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.97,0:10:43.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Cảm...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.24,0:10:48.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ơn—cậu—nhiều.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.10,0:11:15.65,Title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}NONKO-SAN TRONG THẾ NGẶT NGHÈO
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.38,0:11:13.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Về rồi đây!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.30,0:11:16.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Bọn em về rồi đây!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.72,0:11:18.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ô, mừng 2 đứa về.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.47,0:11:21.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Tắm phát thấy khoẻ hẳn ra.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.10,0:11:25.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nói mới nhớ, chưa thấy Nonko-san bước chân ra khỏi nhà trọ Yuragi bao giờ nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.85,0:11:27.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nonko-san ấy nhé...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.60,0:11:28.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Tiên sinh!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.15,0:11:32.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nonko tiên sinh! Em tìm chị nãy giờ đấy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.40,0:11:34.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Rui-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.57,0:11:37.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Không ngờ hạn nộp sát đít rồi mà chị còn có thời gian tắm suối nước nóng.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.69,0:11:40.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Phải cho chị xả hơi chứ.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.28,0:11:42.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nonko... tiên sinh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.28,0:11:46.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Thất lễ rồi, em là khách trọ ở nhà nghỉ Yuragi à?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.29,0:11:54.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Chị là biên tập viên của Arahabaki tiên sinh, tên Harashima Rui.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.63,0:11:56.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Tuần san Thiếu nữ Marmalade?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.21,0:11:58.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Vậy Nonko-san là...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.76,0:12:01.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,hoạ sĩ manga?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.01,0:12:05.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Phải đó, chị có nghề nghiệp đấy nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.10,0:12:07.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Xin phép.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.27,0:12:12.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Xin chào mừng! Dù hơi bừa bộn tí.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.94,0:12:16.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Lúc nào cũng vậy...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.44,0:12:20.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hình như rượu còn nhiều hơn lần trước nữa...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.82,0:12:25.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Vậy vụ "hạn nộp sát đít" là sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.49,0:12:29.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Trợ lý tại gia của Nonko tiên sinh đang được điều trị trong bệnh viện do tai nạn.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.29,0:12:33.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Chắc tuần sau sẽ được xuất viện thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.67,0:12:38.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nhưng mai là hạn nộp bản thảo tháng này rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.05,0:12:40.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mai?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.17,0:12:43.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Chính xác là 7 giờ sáng mai.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.26,0:12:44.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Tức là còn 15 tiếng đồng hồ.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.72,0:12:48.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Vậy mà giờ còn nhiều trang vẫn chưa vẽ.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.89,0:12:51.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Thế này thì tiêu chắc rồi còn gì?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.43,0:12:52.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Tiêu chắc luôn!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.85,0:12:57.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Giúp chị với, Kogarashi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.52,0:12:59.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Thôi được rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.32,0:13:02.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Em cũng sẽ giúp chị hết sức có thể!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.36,0:13:04.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Cảm ơn 2 đứa!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.86,0:13:07.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Chị sẽ cố!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.92,0:13:17.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"Thình thịch, thình thịch, thình thịch..."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.67,0:13:21.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Còn định say đắm cùng 1 người tới khi nào hả?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.13,0:13:23.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nonko-san khác chị nhiều nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.05,0:13:24.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}Hệ tim mạch có bị gì không hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.51,0:13:27.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Khi đang vẽ bản thảo, nhất là trước ngày nộp, chị ấy lại gắt vậy đấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.89,0:13:31.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nhưng mỗi lần bị như thế thì chị ấy lại vẽ kịp thời hạn.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.43,0:13:34.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Lần đầu thấy Nonko-san như thế đấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.35,0:13:38.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Cơ mà, Fuyuzora-kun, em vẽ đẹp đấy chứ.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.52,0:13:40.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Em cũng có vẽ manga à?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.44,0:13:44.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,À không, chỉ là hồi xưa em bị vong của 1 hoạ sĩ manga đầy tham vọng ám thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.90,0:13:45.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Vong?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.82,0:13:52.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nhưng bộ manga này do Nonko-san vẽ, xem ra chị ấy có sở thích khác ngoài rượu nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.37,0:13:55.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nonko-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.46,0:13:59.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Thằng cu này ấy, dù được bao mỹ nhân theo đuổi,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.84,0:14:03.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,nhưng ngoài nữ chính ra, nó chẳng thèm ngó ngàng gì tới vẻ nữ tính của mấy em khác.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.09,0:14:05.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Chả rung động tí nào luôn.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.43,0:14:10.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nhất định nó sẽ không phản bội nữ chính!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.01,0:14:12.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nhất định!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.14,0:14:16.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Trên đời này có loại đàn ông một lòng một dạ như thế ư!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.48,0:14:18.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Chính chị là người vẽ ra thằng đó mà!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.94,0:14:26.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Vì cái đếch gì mà mình phải tạo ra mấy thành phần trẩu tre suốt ngày ve vãn nhau như này chứ?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.57,0:14:29.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Chị đây là người lớn đấy nhé!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.78,0:14:31.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Để chị ấy như thế có sao không vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.91,0:14:36.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nonko tiên sinh hay đưa nỗi niềm của chị ấy vào truyện,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.83,0:14:39.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,lâu lâu nhớ lại thực tại rồi chị ấy thành ra vậy đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.96,0:14:46.93,Default - Italics,NTP,0,0,0,,Hoạ sĩ manga thật là...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.94,0:14:58.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Lần này là chuyện gì thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.44,0:15:01.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Chị bí ở cảnh quấy rối này.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.98,0:15:04.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Chị vẽ phát thảo kém lắm mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.73,0:15:10.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,À, ra là cảnh nhân vật chính bị 1 tên thú tính "tấn công" à?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.20,0:15:12.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Trong shoujo manga có cảnh này nữa à?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.74,0:15:14.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Thì đây là shoujo manga mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.79,0:15:21.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Phải rồi, sẵn có Kogarashi-chan ở đây, cho chị chụp vài tấm làm tư liệu nhé?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.13,0:15:24.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ảnh làm tư liệu ạ?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.51,0:15:31.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nào, Kogarashi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.80,0:15:34.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Tới "xực" chị đi này.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.89,0:15:36.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nghe nguy hiểm quá đấy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.56,0:15:39.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Cơ mà cần phải thay đồ nữa à?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.69,0:15:41.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Làm thế tư liệu mới thêm hữu ích.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.56,0:15:45.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nào, bọn mình bắt đầu "ấy ấy" thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.11,0:15:50.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Kogarashi-chan, đưa tay vòng qua eo chị thêm chút nữa nào.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.79,0:15:59.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Xem ra Fuyuzora-kun không thích chút nào nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.46,0:16:00.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Cũng phải.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.83,0:16:03.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Chị muốn bị quấy rối hơn thế này nữa cơ.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.75,0:16:05.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Em xin lỗi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.71,0:16:10.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Giờ thì, thử cho tay vào váy chị xem.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.89,0:16:14.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,K-Không, chuyện đó thì không được đâu...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.05,0:16:16.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Thiệt là, Kogarashi-chan ấy...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.47,0:16:19.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Không cần xấu hổ vậy đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.56,0:16:22.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Cả chị cũng thấy hơi bẽn lẽn này.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.90,0:16:25.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Đây chỉ là ảnh lấy làm tư liệu thôi mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.53,0:16:30.57,Default - Italics,NTP,0,0,0,,Phải rồi, đây là công việc của Nonko-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.28,0:16:32.70,Default - Italics,NTP,0,0,0,,Phải làm cho đàng hoàng thôi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.53,0:16:35.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Xin lỗi, em lơ đãng quá.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.95,0:16:37.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Em sẽ không do dự nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.33,0:16:38.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Phải khí thế vậy chứ!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.83,0:16:40.37,Default - Italics,NTP,0,0,0,,Cu cậu nghiêm túc thật.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.96,0:16:43.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,V-Vậy em tới đây!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.00,0:16:45.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Không, không!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.54,0:16:46.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,N-Như thế này ạ?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.50,0:16:49.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Phải phải, tuyệt lắm!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.26,0:16:53.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Giờ thì xé áo ngoài của chị ra đi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.47,0:16:54.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Vâng!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.14,0:16:56.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- Đẩy chị lên giường đi!\N- Vâng!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.81,0:17:09.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- X-Xin lỗi!\N- Đừng có bỏ ra chứ!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.65,0:17:13.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Này, Rui-san, chụp 1 cảnh góc cao đằng này với đằng này.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.20,0:17:14.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Vâng!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.03,0:17:16.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Thay đổi góc chụp tí để được nhiều mẫu!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.20,0:17:17.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Đã rõ!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.70,0:17:19.62,Default - Flashback,NTP,0,0,0,,"Đây... là người lớn à?!"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.66,0:17:24.58,Default - Flashback,NTP,0,0,0,,Kogarashi có hơi cảm-phục chị ấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.92,0:17:28.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nhân đây mình chụp ảnh tham khảo cho cảnh lễ hội văn hoá luôn nhé?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.84,0:17:30.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ý hay đó!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.76,0:17:35.43,Default - Flashback,NTP,0,0,0,,Tuy nhiên, tới nửa đêm thì...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.31,0:17:41.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Đã nửa đêm rồi à?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.22,0:17:43.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nãy giờ bản thảo vẫn chưa được chút nào cả!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.60,0:17:46.77,Default - Flashback,NTP,0,0,0,,"Minh sẽ không bao giờ trở thành loại người lớn như thế!"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.48,0:17:50.36,Default - Flashback,NTP,0,0,0,,Cu cậu đã thề với chính mình vậy đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.53,0:17:56.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Em pha cho chị cốc cà phê này.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.91,0:17:58.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Cảm ơn em.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.53,0:18:01.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Có nên gọi chị ấy dậy không ạ?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.91,0:18:05.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Sau khi bản thảo hoàn thành mới là lúc Rui-chan thực sự làm việc.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.75,0:18:08.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nhưng nhờ em ấy mà chị mới làm kịp được.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.79,0:18:09.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Thế thì tốt.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.92,0:18:12.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Em không biết chuyện rồi sẽ ra sao nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.38,0:18:19.10,Default - Italics,NTP,0,0,0,,Nói mới nhớ, trong khi vẽ manga, chị ấy không hề uống rượu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.10,0:18:24.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nonko-san, chị yêu công việc này thật nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.52,0:18:27.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Chị cũng chẳng biết nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.48,0:18:35.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Thật ra hồi xưa chị cũng từng đi tiêu diệt yêu quái như Sagi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.90,0:18:37.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Có chuyện đó ạ?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.53,0:18:44.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Chuyện đó giống như số mệnh định sẵn cho hậu duệ của quỷ vậy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.79,0:18:52.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hồi xưa, chị là một cô gái tốt lắm đó, và như chị vừa nói, chị đã cố hết sức chiến đấu với yêu quái.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.80,0:19:02.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nhưng đến một ngày, chị gặp chuyện rồi bị thương rất nặng, lúc đó chị đã nghĩ...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.06,0:19:08.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"A, cuộc đời mình sẽ chấm dứt như thế này ư, mình vẫn chưa làm được gì hết mà..."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.11,0:19:13.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Có lẽ những chuyện xảy ra sau đó chính là kết quả của suy nghĩ đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.32,0:19:17.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nếu không được làm những gì mình thích thì chị thấy rất áy náy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.49,0:19:24.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Chị đã kinh qua rất nhiều công việc, và rốt cuộc chị đã quyết định làm nghề này.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.71,0:19:33.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nhưng có lẽ rốt cuộc, chị chỉ đang trốn chạy việc chiến đấu thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.21,0:19:39.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Không, em không nghĩ vậy đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.72,0:19:46.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Bởi Nonko-san, chị có thể vì chuyện tiêu diệt yêu quái mà kiềm bớt lại không?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.27,0:19:50.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Chuyện uống rượu ấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.82,0:19:56.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Tiên sinh...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.37,0:20:07.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Xem ra chị không làm được rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.25,0:20:11.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Giờ thì!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.83,0:20:13.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,2 tiếng nữa là tới hạn nộp!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.92,0:20:17.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Vẽ xong bản thảo rồi đi tắm với làm 1 chầu nào!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.30,0:20:26.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Đã nhận được bản thảo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.85,0:20:30.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Vậy em đi đây!\NCả tháng qua chị đã vất vả rồi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.94,0:20:35.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Xong rồi, em vất vả rồi...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.52,0:20:39.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Vậy em đi ngủ đây.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.70,0:20:44.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Cạn ly!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.79,0:20:53.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Vẽ xong bản thảo mà làm 1 chầu bia thì còn gì bằng!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.38,0:20:55.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Không không, chị định nhậu ngay bây giờ luôn ạ?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.38,0:20:56.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Em muốn đi ngủ cơ!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.92,0:21:00.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Có sao đâu, chị đã cố gắng lắm cơ mà!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.63,0:21:05.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- Ăn mừng cùng nhau nào!\N- Khoan! Chị say rồi à?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.43,0:21:08.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Em mà không đồng ý là chị hổng thả ra đâu!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.35,0:21:10.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Em biết rồi, biết rồi mà...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.18,0:21:14.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nonko-san, biên tập viên của em đi rồi kìa.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.56,0:21:16.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Việc xong chưa em?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.23,0:21:19.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mọi người, chào buổi sáng!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.53,0:21:26.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Fuyuzora Kogarashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.83,0:21:28.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ngươi làm gì ở đây hả?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.54,0:21:30.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Tui chỉ tới giúp thôi mà!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.45,0:21:32.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Sagiri-san, chờ đã!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.33,0:21:34.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nhất định Nonko-san lại say nữa rồi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.50,0:21:35.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Được rồi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.08,0:21:39.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Vậy mọi người cùng ăn mừng luôn nào!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.01,0:21:41.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Sao lại cởi hết đồ ra thế kia?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.63,0:21:44.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mỗi lần làm xong việc là em ấy lại vậy đấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.97,0:21:48.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nào! Làm thêm chầu nữa nào!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.30,0:21:51.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nonko-san, mặc đồ vào dùm em cái!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.56,0:21:56.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mọi người cùng cởi đồ luôn thì tốt chứ sao!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.15,0:22:00.32,Default - Flashback,NTP,0,0,0,,Kogarashi vẫn chưa biết rằng sau này, cu cậu sẽ còn bị kéo vào...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.32,0:22:03.32,Default - Flashback,NTP,0,0,0,,mấy tình thế còn ngặt nghèo hơn nữa.
